				<text><![CDATA[          



          The staff of                                                                      has submitted their Hand Receipt

towards reimbursement of office expenses incurred by them wide statement inclosed separately 

for Rs.

                  

          The nature of expenses incurred by them (viz) cost of newspaper supplied to the residence of

officers,Auto fare,Bus fare, Train ticket cancellation charges, Binding, Xerox, Telephone cleaning 

charges pocket allowence to drivers etc.,

                 

          The said expenditure has to be debited to the Head of Account 

                  

          The Budget Estimate for the finanacial year                    under the Head of the A/C is Rs.      

cost of bills a sum of Rs.                          has been incurred so far and balance amount of Rs.                   

is available as Contingent.


                 
          Hence it is submitted for orders whether the bill may be admitted for payment of Rs.                          

                  

          Subject for orders on X above a draft payment order is put up below for approval please.]]></text>
				</staticText>
